directions: This is in the movie theater after the ticket counter.  If you go past the restrooms at the entrance make a right and go past the ticket counter there is a family restroom down the hall and make a right.  It will be on the left side.  It’s a private handicapped accessible family restroom.  I’m disabled and I’ve been there many times and they are very nice about using it even if you don’t have a ticket they will let you use it.
